{"tid":5910,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】真莖不怕球練　他用陰莖屌打乒乓","createTime":"2016-11-27T06:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T06:15:05.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7030fcb8eef0cde1e331abc77e2409ae2b895173","tid":5910,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"國外推特在這兩天瘋傳一段影片，一名金髮男子以全裸之姿，與友人一同打乒乓球。更令人吃驚的是，這名男子不用球拍，而是以生殖器代替球拍，「屌打」乒乓。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，相信這段影片是在本周二晚間於推特上流傳開來，已經有超過19000名網友對該影片按讚了。對於該名男子的「能力」，獲得許多網友讚賞，網友「@ShaunK98」就說：「我從沒見過這麼厲害的。」網友「@_ladyloki」：「控制得真好，也太好笑。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/column/article/9/rnews/20160129/785947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F9%2Frnews%2F20160129%2F785947&d=RRFyPJExOFzaatkg3WeVH8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f61b3a1d\" target=\"_blank\">m.appledaily.com.tw/column/article/9/rnews/20160129/785947</a>"},{"pid":"f3598e98760631aa37e7eabf6c7403ab072b35f7","tid":5910,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}